{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC07_MAR_030.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x2c,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xe9,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "*sigh* Maybe staking out this place is just a waste of time..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "This is the only sizable town in the area. I am sure he will need supplies eventually."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x167,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "So would he not show himself in this town sooner or later?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xed,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Logically, that should be true, but this isn't our only job, remember?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "A stakeout is meaningless if we can't constantly keep an eye out."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Besides, it's just ridiculous that we need to search for someone in a foreign nation, without a portrait."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Could the people from headquarters be hazing us...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Marion and Linca, are you investigating today, as well?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Well, today's job is more about<CR>searching for a certain person,<CR>rather than our usual job."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Actually, Ayesha, perfect timing! I have something I wanna ask you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Do not worry, it will not take long."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Okay, if that's the case..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Well, headquarters is looking for a certain person...and I got this wanted poster..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Huh!? A f-f-fugitive!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "I don't have a lot of acquaintances,<CR>so I doubt the fugitive is someone I<CR>know..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Just listen, we only have the personal history of this guy. We don't even have a sketch of his face."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "But I thought maybe you would know."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, okay. I'm not sure if I can help you or not though."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Thank you. The wanted person's name is Keithgriff Hazeldine."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "He's in his mid-40s, tall and lean,<CR>with silver hair and a mustache. Oh,<CR>and he's always smoking cigarettes."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "And...this is the biggest point.<CR>This wanted guy is an alchemist,<CR>just like you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "An alchemist...? Me...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Umm, what's an alchemist? Other people have called me that before, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Huh? You don't know? I wonder if they call it something different around here..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, even I know what alchemists are."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "People call someone like you, an alchemist."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Wha‐!? I'm an alchemist...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xeb,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Linca, your explanation doesn't explain anything."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xed,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "It's someone who's acquainted with various materials and possesses the skill to create and transform them..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Creating precious metals from base metals, or delving into the power that dwells in natural objects for cures..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "See? It's the same as what you're doing. That skill is called alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "S-So that's what it is... I didn't even know."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Hmm...but I still think of myself as an apothecary..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "It seems like you don't understand the greatness of your skills."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "I know! I have the perfect book for you, so you can have it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "It's a book on alchemy. I think you'll be able to take advantage of it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1a5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "Wow, thank you so much. And, I'm sorry for making you feel concerned about me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "Don't worry. In return, if you figure anything out about this wanted man, let me know."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x41,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "Well Linca, let's say it's another job done and go home for today."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x19b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "Okay. Ayesha, I will see you again."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "(Wow, I got a nice book. I should read it right away when I get back.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "(Still, a wanted person.<CR>In his 40s, with silver hair,<CR>a mustache, and cigarettes...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "msg_string": "(Wait a minute...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You got the book: Alchemy Basics."
        }
    ]
}